    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Teddy on his sprawling adventure as he navigates treacherous paths and impossible hurdles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over<strong> </strong><strong><u>60</u></strong><strong> stages,</strong> each presenting a unique challenge. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164520/extras/9c3f07e43b8d50cab38a57cf02971c5b.poster.avif?t=1764860875\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164520/extras/9c3f07e43b8d50cab38a57cf02971c5b.webm?t=1764860875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164520/extras/9c3f07e43b8d50cab38a57cf02971c5b.mp4?t=1764860875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure Teddy stays on the rolling ball, as strange figures seek to knock him off balance and push him aside. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164520/extras/fef45e9430f52be7b055db7af792b071.poster.avif?t=1764860875\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164520/extras/fef45e9430f52be7b055db7af792b071.webm?t=1764860875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164520/extras/fef45e9430f52be7b055db7af792b071.mp4?t=1764860875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fun physics-based arcade experience awaits, that has plenty of twists, turns and surprises. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive controls ensure smooth navigation. Simply speed up or slow down, move right and left. The game is easy to learn, but tough to master. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by fun games from the 90s, with updated visuals and retro-themed game design that focuses on gameplay. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game targets a native 100-120FPS. </p></li></ul>",
